Pre-Game Insights: Australia have a bright chance for the semi-finals, while England are at the bottom of the table and need to win their remaining games to qualify for the ICC Champions Trophy 2025.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The pitch at Narendra Modi Stadium offers a great batting track where big totals are normal, but under lights, the ball tends to seam and swing more.
Others: Australia hold an edge with 87 victories as compared to England's 63 in their head-to-head records.
